Dragon - In a desperate attempt to save her kingdom from an advancing army of dark elves, Princess Vanir must traverse the haunted forest of Sidhe. With the help of loyal adventurers Cador and Artemir, they encounter the army of elves, a mysterious sorceress, and the powerful dragon that stands in their way.

2006
Stars: Amelia Jackson-Gray, Matthew Wolf, Jon-Paul Gates
